I know it is a teleport as I know someone on our server managed to trick a hapless guide into using his Guide key on it and watched as he got ported to Lesser Fay..<br>
But there is an added mystery to the area where the pot is....<br>
If you turn left, walk up to the wall and sit (with the new models, I dont think this trick works with the old) you catch a glimpse through the wall of a tunnel heading down. <br>
After I spotted this I wandered around to see if I could get a better view of this tunnel through another wall, and I found it.<br>
In the Dining room above the area where the Cultural Armour Vendor is there are Sconces on the wall, if you get your head in the right spot you get a clear view of the Tunnel in Question.<br>
I speculate this is the way to an unfinished 4th Gate in Neriak, probably where the King and Queen of the Dark Elves Reside. It more than likely has been there all along, just never been opened or finished.<br>
